Statement from Solenn Entertainment üî∑Ô∏èSubject: Dissemination of Fake News and Misleading Information ‚û°Ô∏è In reference to the recent circulation of messages and information on social media platforms that distort facts and spread false allegations concerning Freen-Sarocha Chankimha, an artist under Solenn Entertainment, the company would like to clarify that all such information is entirely untrue. The content being circulated has no connection whatsoever to any individual, event, or location mentioned in those claims. ‚û°Ô∏èThe creation, alteration, or dissemination of such false information constitutes a violation of personal rights and has caused damage to the artist's reputation. Solenn Entertainment and the artist will take strict legal action, both criminal and civil, against any individual or group involved in creating, publishing, or forwarding such false information. The company has already gathered relevant evidence for use in the judicial process. Solenn Entertainment respectfully requests the public and media to refrain from sharing or forwarding any unverified information that has not been officially confirmed by the company, in order to prevent further misunderstanding and harm to the parties involved. #srchafreen #freensarocha #solennentertainment #freenbecky #thaigl
